I think this is the right channel for this, I have a question about the Ops Hub Webhook action. I am getting the following warning when I run a test: `Testing results include invalid JSON` .  The response from <http://webhook.site|webhook.site> looks like this:
```statusCode: 200
contentType: application/json
body: "{"hs_execution_state":"SUCCESS"}"```
The webhook is going out fine, but I would really like to be able to parse the response. Any idea whats happening here? Even if I return a blank response I get the warning, I would like to be able to branch data in the body.
Hello! Is there any update on CBE data use in a workflow?
